oDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-T%E1%BB%AD-Chi/Thanh-b%C3%ACnh-nh%E1%BA%A1c/poem-kRtrE__MQIYvGOLSePWIMQ">Thanh bình nhạc - 清平樂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-T%E1%BB%AD-Chi/author-nzYvzfRmo_6cp61oWHXvHg">Chu Tử Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Tho%E1%BA%A1i-t%C4%83ng/poem-EOPtnofrA0CAZ87o-6sPGA">Thoại tăng - 話僧</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%C3%ACnh-vi%E1%BB%87n/poem-Hsh3mfR2BwkxDQ3k4O8Lbg">Tình viện - 晴院</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAm-Ph%E1%BB%A5c/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-S%C3%A0i-Trang-Khanh-xu%E1%BA%A5t-s%E1%BB%A9-An-Nam/poem--jdViBeNbIjfuZReiFPbZw">Tống thượng thư Sài Trang Khanh xuất sứ An Nam - 送尚書柴莊卿出使安南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAm-Ph%E1%BB%A5c/author-fEYQmxvOXn6VD3zSg5pFrQ">Diêm Phục</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
